          "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_01.mp3",
          "text": "So what do you plan on doing once I pull them in?",
          "duration": 3.205
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_02.mp3",
          "text": "I, push them away\u2026",
          "duration": 1.913
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Bebop",
          "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_03.mp3",
          "text": "That kind of defeats the purpose of me pulling them in, right?",
          "duration": 3.205
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_04.mp3",
          "text": "Kind of, yes.",
          "duration": 1.843
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "character": "Bebop",
          "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_05",
          "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_05.mp3",
          "text": "This isn't going to go well is it.",
          "duration": 2.068
        },
        {
          "order": 6,
          "character": "Doorman",
          "audioFile": "doorman_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_06",
          "audioUrl": "audio/doorman_match_start_doorman_bebop_convo02_06.mp3",
          "text": "Not the ideal pairing, no, but I'm sure we can make it work.",
          "duration": 4.939
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "bebop_doorman_convo03",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
